                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; a few groups of lines (alternating with black lines) on the incipit pages of Texts I-III; two or three lines of the incipits of daily readings and their sections in Texts I-III; text dividers; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.</rubric>
